title: Necrodome [PC] [ENGLISH] [FULL]
description:
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS


Mount and Install Necrodome. (Maximum Install)


NOTE


Works on Windows XP (in Windows 95 Compatibility mode)


I don't know if Necrodome works on Win 7 or 8 so please don't ask me. If you really like this game then download it and try it. If it doesn't work on newer operating systems then you can only play it in a virtual machine like VMWare running Windows XP under Windows 95 Compatibility mode.


Enjoy & Seed!
